                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3 group-hover:text-green-600 dark:group-hover:text-green-400 transition-colors">Time Series Forecasting with Nepal Stock Exchange (NEPSE) Dataset</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-md leading-relaxed mb-6">● Performed time-series forecasting on NEPSE (Nepal Stock Exchange) data, leveraging statistical and machine learning models to predict market trends and evaluate predictive performance.</p>

